---
import DownloadButtons from '@/components/download-buttons.astro'
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 pb-16 md:px-0 lg:pb-24">
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] card-brand px-6 py-16 sm:px-12 sm:py-20">
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-20 -right-20 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-accent-coral/25 blur-3xl animate-blob"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-16 -left-16 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-accent-mint/20 blur-3xl animate-blob animation-delay-300"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 h-48 w-48 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-accent-violet/15 blur-3xl animate-glow"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 animate-fade-up">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-3xl">
          <span class="text-gradient-vivid">
            Следи за финансами и временем в одном приложении
          </span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-subtle">
          Простой интерфейс, никаких оплат или сторонних сервисов. Приложение создано для
          удобства без лишних заморочек
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
        <DownloadButtons />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
